introWebside.text02: In August, due to Claudia's parents' health situation, we decided to move the four-year-old dog Kica to Switzerland. Kica receives an extensive veterinary medical examination and, in accordance with the Swiss Pet Recommendations, an identification chip. In addition, the vaccination status is checked or supplemented.
introWebside.text04: After a few training trips in Portugal, Kica traveled with the Agostini family - Sissy, Matthiasm Joana, Raul and Alena in the family bus from Montecordova to Basel on September 8th and was warmly welcomed by Claudia at her new home on Binzenstrasse.
introWebside.text06: At first it was just a vague idea - but then it was quickly confirmed: Kica brought us a little surprise package - she was pregnant with six little puppies.
